Thanks for this repost.... 

This short film was my first (and only) attempt to use different forms of symbolism within the video context. For some reason I felt 'compelled' to attempt a piece like this. I had a lot of fun making it and I sincerely hope you enjoy viewing it.
BTW.... Thanks for the kind words, M  :)
